sql:
SELECT SUM(ae.value) AS total_engagement
FROM audience_engagement ae
WHERE ae.production_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "Films" refer to productions of type 'film';
- "Total audience engagement" is calculated by summing the engagement values for each film;
- "Since 1990" means the production started after the year 1990.
